      "content": "sometimes i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back. it feels like the real me—the one with actual dreams and a future—died a long time ago. now i’m just walking around in this shell, just a ghost of who i was supposed to be. it's exhausting being a corpse that still has to breathe.",
